snippet.title: Johnny Depp Arrives In Court For 'The Sun' Lawsuit
snippet.description:
After Johnny Depp made a surprise appearance at court, Roz Weston and Graeme O'Neil discuss his lawsuit against "The Sun" for calling him a "wife-beater" during "ET Canada Live".
